      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "PF"                 to   p-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   p-tip                  .
           move      132                  to   p-car                  .
           move      p-lnr                to   p-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   p-pos                  .
           move      " Data reg.  Data docum.   Codice   Ragione sociale
      -              "                                Imponibile   %    
      -              "     Imposta    Totale documento"
                                          to   p-alf                  .
